bug.short_desc: The qooxdoo playground does not work with Firefox 19

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1219 Screenshot
The qooxdoo playground does not run in Firefox 19 - see attached screenshot.
Firefox 19 will be released in February 2013, an early developer version can already be downloaded.
I do not think that this issue is a Firefox bug, since most parts of a big javascript app are running well in Firefox 19.

Same root cause.
